@startuml
' Filename: Drive_System_StateDiagram.plantuml
' Diagram Type: State Diagram
' Authored 2026-07-18 from the live engine: src/simulation/drive-agent.ts
' (evaluateFirmwareInternalDriveState) + behavior/drive-decay.ts (evaluateDriveState).
'
' The dual-drive (O/P) machine. Both O and P increment every tick; a successful
' reinforcement decrements the dominant drive. The state is a pure function of
' (levelO, levelP) against (lowerLimit, upperLimit) — the firmware internal_drive_state
' code 1..4. Note: unlike a classic FSM, transitions are re-evaluated every tick from
' the current levels, so any state can be reached from any other as the levels cross.

[*] --> BothSatisfied

state "1 · satisfied-and-indifferent" as BothSatisfied {
  ' lowerLimit > levelO  AND  lowerLimit > levelP
  ' driveSearch = Neither -> outcome satisfied-and-indifferent
}

state "2 · O search (O dominant)" as OSearch {
  ' levelO > levelP  ->  driveSearch = O
}

state "3 · P search (P dominant)" as PSearch {
  ' levelP > levelO  ->  driveSearch = P
}

state "4 · either-O-or-P (both desperate / tied)" as EitherSearch {
  ' (levelO > upperLimit AND levelP > upperLimit)  OR  levelO == levelP
  ' driveSearch = OP -> outcome either-search
}

BothSatisfied --> OSearch : O rises, O > P
BothSatisfied --> PSearch : P rises, P > O
BothSatisfied --> EitherSearch : both rise past upper limit, or O == P
OSearch --> PSearch : P overtakes O
PSearch --> OSearch : O overtakes P
OSearch --> EitherSearch : both > upper limit, or O == P
PSearch --> EitherSearch : both > upper limit, or O == P
EitherSearch --> OSearch : O > P after a decrement
EitherSearch --> PSearch : P > O after a decrement
OSearch --> BothSatisfied : dominant drive decremented below the lower limit
PSearch --> BothSatisfied : dominant drive decremented below the lower limit
EitherSearch --> BothSatisfied : drive decremented below the lower limit

legend right
  The dominant drive level (max of O, P) is broadcast as this unit's
  act_drive_level (0..168) — the beam's arbitration weight. See src/simulation/drive-agent.ts.
endlegend

@enduml
